**Components Used**:
- `ERC20Upgradeable`: Base token functionality
- `ERC20BurnableUpgradeable`: Token burning capability
- `ERC20PausableUpgradeable`: Emergency pause functionality
- `ERC20VotesUpgradeable`: Governance voting capabilities
- `AccessControlUpgradeable`: Role-based access control
- `UUPSUpgradeable`: Proxy upgrade mechanism
- `ReentrancyGuardUpgradeable`: Reentrancy attack protection
- `PausableUpgradeable`: Pausable functionality for staking contract
- `TimelockControllerUpgradeable`: Governance timelock

**Modifications**: No modifications made to OpenZeppelin code. Used as-is via inheritance.

**Security Audits**: OpenZeppelin contracts are professionally audited. See: https://docs.openzeppelin.com/contracts/5.x/#security

